### Pair Programming - **Student Side**

Students will need to follow the instructions below to pair program with up to four other students in the same class section.

**Note:**  Pairing for students depends on one of the following login types you chose for you class section:

1. Class section login type with secret word/picture based passwords.
2. Class section login type with personal email, Google Classroom, and Clever.

### 1. Secret Word/Picture Based Password Sections

Students will see the images below when they log into your class section.  If a student checks "I have a partner at my computer" and then signs in, they will be given the option to choose a partner.

